##We wait with the trapped pet until the owner returns to Earth

Micro Signal thelivings

The function introduction, reconstructs our life with the narrative beauty.

I even thought it would be nice if everything was just a false alarm. There is no epidemic, no virus, no cousin of the far away from home, there is no countless owners and pets of the far side.

Photo: still from why cats can't bark

"those bastards are the ones who hurt my ashes! "
On January 30th, I was horrified by the pictures of my closest friends -- a masked security guard with a menacing look on his face, clutching a cat with bloody hind legs and gloved hands.
I quickly sent her a private message. On wechat, a tearful friend said, "the property owners said that cats and dogs spread COVID-19. This morning, when my ashes came out, they took a shovel and slapped it. "
"Look at the back paws. They're covered in blood. Are they human? Can online rumors be true? " Her best friend cried.
I can only comfort her, "don't worry, ash will get better. "
The girl friend is more excited: "I have called the police, but the police can tell me, 'you are not worth this cat anyway, big deal another one. "
Speaking of which, the Bestie is in tears. For her best friend, gray is not just a kitten, but her only "relative" out there, "You know what? I work overtime every day, the cold home only ash waiting for me. When I was sick, no one in bed, only ash with its warm body to warm me. "
Bestie burst into tears, then complained about the property, then cursed those who eat wild animals idiot, toss all night.
The next day, as I was about to call her, I got a screenshot of the conversation from my best friend as soon as I turned on my phone.
Bestie in the owners of the group, someone deliberately sent an article on the cat and dog disease, now the property is a few owners, together with the fierce vindictive Bestie it. "How can some people be so selfish and still have the face to call the police? Is it cats and dogs that are important or people's lives that are important? " The property owner Point at the Mulberry Tree while cursing the locust tree
Other owners also follow scold up: "Dog Bite LV Dongbin, do not know the heart of a good person! Others property that is responsible for you, responsible for us all. "
In the rumors, the three of them become tigers, insist that all cats and dogs are the source of infection. It wasn't until a few days later, when a rumor surfaced online that the World Health Organization was denying the story, that the farce finally came to an end. Of course, none of them apologized to their girlfriends, and the group Poker Face as if it had never happened.
Only the bestie embrace the dying gray, red eye asked me: "Now who can compensate me a healthy gray? "
Gray dust from a best friend's home

Gray's unfortunate encounter, make me both angry and regret. Not long after, I had a little teddy in my house, as if she were a baby.
The dog-loving cousin had always posed as a "mother" to her precious Teddy. However, February 3 that day, cousin but personally her"penis"sent to my home.
The cousin smiled and said: "This little fellow temporarily entrusted to you. ". Just received the notice today, the hospital told us to leave for Wuhan the day after tomorrow. I'm the head of the smoking department, and I'm supposed to be first in line. Don't worry, I'm proud of it."My mother listened to her cousin's advice, sobbing quietly, he held the teddy and muttered, "Mutt, why don't you stop your mother? You tell her her aunt can't talk to her family and tell her not to leave. "
The more my mother talked, the more she felt sad. Finally, she grabbed my cousin's arm and blocked the door, "Girl, I beg you, do not go? At worst, we do not become a doctor, I will find you another job. If not, you live in my home, aunt to support you for life... "
My cousin had to persuade my mother again.
My cousin's Teddy
At the thought of my cousin going to the front line, and the virus close hand-to-hand combat, my mother her old man every day at home to burn incense worship, pray for Buddha to bless cousin safe return. Sometimes I would wake up in the middle of the night and cry at the Little Teddy. My mother has Neurasthenia, and she used to have trouble sleeping, and now she has trouble getting enough sleep.

One day at noon, she even told me suspiciously that there was always a strange noise on the balcony of the house next door. At first, I didn't care. I thought she was just nervous and hearing voices. It wasn't until noon that I heard a series of whimsical "chirps" as I passed the balcony. Even my own Teddy, fanning his ears warily, followed me out onto the balcony. But when we rushed to the past, only to find that the next balcony clearly nothing, and the sound is getting louder and louder.
"Is someone playing a practical joke? "
Puzzled, I brought my stool and stood looking up at the balcony next door. This one look, be really frightened not light. His balcony was littered with dried urine and rotting food, and scattered bits and pieces of dog shit.
The next moment, a tiny, shivering ball, she slipped through the sliding glass door into the balcony, as if she were a puppy!
"What about his owner? How can he leave the dog alone? Is he crazy? "
Then my mother remembered that the family had said they were going back to their hometown in Hubei Province for the New Year.
"Is it Hubei? " I feel something bad, to the property to the owner of the dog's phone, this just know he is really because of the city is trapped in Wuhan.
"What about your dog? " I asked anxiously.
The dog's owner's tone was full of despair: "leave it to chance. When I left, I left him some water and dog food. Maybe... maybe he can hold on until I come back. But can I come back... "
It turned out that the owner's parents had been infected with COVID-19, are admitted to the hospital, the father or critically ill patients. He's in such a mess right now, he has no time for the family dog.
On second thought, I decided to rescue the poor thing. But whether throwing food through the air, or hanging dog food with a stick, because the two balcony distance is too large and declared failure.
I even thought of climbing a ladder between two balconies. But I live on the fifth floor. It's too risky. After intense thought struggle, I decided to put on glasses and mask, go downstairs to find some handy tools, the results were just out of the aunt on patrol stopped
Aunt thought I was going out of the community, immediately criticized me. His tone softened when he heard about the dog. Aunt gave me advice and said: "behind the first building there is a long bamboo pole, which is used when they dredge the well, about 2 meters long, you go to get it. "
I took the bamboo pole home, tied a ham intestines, just sent to the hungry little thing will be two eyes, like the Arrow from the string, rushed over. The little one gobbled it up and then wagged his tail excitedly at me and spun around in place for several times.
I was relieved to see him jumping around.

Soon, I began to think about another question, how many other pets in our city are trapped in their homes, waiting to die like this? And will the little ones survive the sudden onslaught?
That day, the neighborhood aunt also inadvertently mentioned that the next community also has a family because of home, four trustees to take her cat. As she spoke, she shook her head again and again. "We don't have many pet homes here. Now there are rumors of cat-and-dog diseases. Who would dare take in her cat? "
"What happened then? "
"What can I do? Throw the cat away. " The old woman sighed heavily. "Oh, what a sin! The kitten is only a few months old, and now the weather is so cold, it must not survive. "
After listening to aunt's words, my heart could not help shaking for a while. I also understand that most people are preoccupied at the moment, so it's natural to be more concerned about the daily price of food and the supply of masks than about pets. The outbreak is so overwhelming, it's understandable, but I still feel a deep sense of helplessness.
Local pet bars on the Internet are full of complaints, and the shoveling officers are in all kinds of trouble.
Someone worried, his home British short pregnancy 2 months, may be about to give birth. But now he is out of town, simply can not buy a ticket back to the city;
Some people want to cry without tears, since she was sent to the hotel isolation observation, the home of the Dutch pig will no longer care, now has been hungry for six whole days, I do not know whether dead or alive;
Others were willing to pay $500 a pop for someone to take care of a pond full of SCIADOPITYS Verticillata Koi in their yard. "That's my life. ".
Through this line for help, I seem to see behind the screen, countless pet owners worried and helpless expression. So, when I learned that our city also set up a pet support group, I immediately decided to join.

Pet Mutual group owners is an 85, is also a senior racing pigeon enthusiasts, he raised the plum age pigeon (a racing pigeon) has been a number of provincial awards.
My first task was to rescue the Hamster: the owner told me that a hamster owner found him yesterday, said the hamster left at home may be sick, want me to help. I immediately contacted the owner of the hamster, the little girl just received the phone, they began to cry. "Auntie, please go and see Maman. She has a bad eye. She is ill... " she pleaded
Manman is the name of the hamster, before the whole family left home, because of the hamster because of fire, eye some inflammation. Now the family are in the field, the hamster no one to take care of, the little girl is very worried.
I consoled the little girl and asked for her home address. At first, I thought I would have to ask the master to pick the lock. The girl's mother told me that she had hidden a spare key in front of the house before she left, which greatly reduced my troubles. According to the address they gave me, I found her house. In order to avoid suspicion, from the door after entering the home, all the way open wechat video.
When the little girl saw Mann from the video, suddenly "Wow" , burst into tears, it is no wonder that the little girl will be sad, the hamster is so miserable. His eyes were red and Puffy, and his left eye was so bulging that it looked like he had pinkeye.
The little girl touched the screen and burst into tears. "Manman, what's wrong with you? What's wrong with you? "
I picked him up gingerly, feeling his four little legs shaking and afraid he wouldn't be able to stay at home alone. After asking permission, I decided to take memnon back to my home to take care of him.
| Hamster "Manman" (photo by the author)
I asked the Little Girl's mother: "Hamsters can use my usual drops of chloramphenicol eye drops? " After receiving a positive response, my hamster doctor immediately on the job.
First, I took a cotton swab from my ear, dipped it in salt water, carefully cleaned the hair around the eye socket for the little hamster, and then stretched out its eyelids, took out the chloramphenicol eye drops, to its two small eyes, each drop half a drop. Little hamsters are very afraid of animals, I was arrested, always in a state of panic. Once, when I had just put eye drops on him, he shivered and shivered and doused my hands with a hot bath of rat urine. It made me laugh and cry.
The only good thing about memnon is that he's not picky. Whether I handed it cabbage leaves, cabbage, melon seeds, red lentils, it all according to orders. Each time will use those two dexterous mouse claws, a take food, embrace in the arms happily nibble.
For the next few days, the three of US skyped with me almost every day. The little girl saw her hamster gradually recovered, his face has gradually a smile, always sweet to call me "aunt" , over and over to thank me.

So, with my cousin Teddy, the dog next door that I had to take care of every day, and a hamster, I was finally a proud zookeeper.
At first, my mother didn't approve of me volunteering to adopt animals, but when she saw the poor little ones, she relented. However, my mother and I still "rule three" , said that from now on, except for special circumstances, can not bring home small animals; and out of safety considerations, let me try to only take care of pets in the neighborhood. I gave my mother what she wanted.
When I got up, I was so busy that I fed the hamster red lentils, then the little Teddy, then the neighbor's dog with a bamboo pole.
It's busy, but it's fun.
Lantern Festival, at noon I was at home to eat Yuanxiao, wechat suddenly rang up. The host smiled and exchanged greetings with me: "Happy Lantern Festival, how many dumplings have you eaten today? "
"The Lord of the flock, you still straight to the point, direct address. " I certainly understand the intention of the Lord of the Flock, "this time is what community? "
"In xx Geum River, there is a black cockatoo on the first floor of unit 3. The owner said the corn for the cockatoo is on the balcony. You can jump over the wall and into his courtyard from the street next to the community. "
"All right! "
I hung up the phone and rode my scooter straight to the neighborhood. Came to the back door of the community on the street, I took a deep breath, carefully stepped on the garbage can, ready to jump over the wall.
However, I was about to make a move when a shout came from behind: "who? COME DOWN QUICKLY! "
As I turned in a panic, I saw two street-level disease-seekers running toward me in a menacing manner. Left and right, they quickly closed in on me. One of them glared at me and said, "I can't believe it's a female thief! Tell me honestly, how many houses have you stolen? What other neighborhoods have you been to? "
I quickly explained: "No, you are mistaken, I am the master of the House to take care of the parrot. "
"What Parrot? You made that up. "
"I have no key and the Parrot's owner is out of town, so I decided to climb over the wall. "
The interviewer is still a look suspicious, until they use the phone contact with the community property, and through the community property to the parrot owner verification, finally solved the misunderstanding.
"young man, " said one of the visitors, with a sigh, "it's too dangerous for you to do this. We've talked to the landlord, and they can feed the parrot from now on. "
"Okay. " I let out a long sigh of relief and quickly thanked them.
When I got home, I told the group about how I had nearly been mistaken for a thief. We laughed and shared some of the weirdest things we've ever done with our pets.
"actually, I was asked to volunteer to provide epsilon's canned salmon. Those cat cans cost 28 yuan for 170 grams. Do you really think all of us volunteers are rich people? " We are obliged to help animals, but the owners of the animals'expenses are usually passed on to us.
Li Jie is also very speechless: "The day before yesterday, someone asked me about mealworms, I said we only save animals, not insects. ". He said there is no mealworm, you save the turtles, Goldfish eat it? And then he taught me about feeding mealworms. Later I realized that the mealworm he was talking about was actually a common mealworm."
The owner also said he had promised to help feed the dog, and did not ask about the breed of dog, only known as Xiaomengmeng. He thought it must be a small Chihuahua, but as soon as he opened the gate that day, he was spotted by a fierce, snarling, barking dog, "What Little Baby? It's a big black back! If it wasn't for the chain, you wouldn't have seen me. "
Since then, the owners have been so traumatized that they have made it a point to report the breed. However, afraid to return, he was still unable to stand up to a distant relative's rough and tumble, took his relative's Teddy back to his home in Florida during that time, because the epidemic did not want to go home, and extended the length of time on the other side, leaving the masters helpless.

Oddly enough, little teddy's belly had gotten bigger and bigger since he'd been in the family home. At first none of us cared, thinking Teddy had just put on a few pounds. But with the passage of time, its stomach actually like blowing balloons, from time to time will vomit, how to look like a pregnancy reaction.
The owner was no longer calm and asked me in a panic, "is your Teddy always like this? Is it... is it an accidental pregnancy? " I also asked its owner, my relatives said do not know
I frowned and nodded. "I think I am pregnant. My cousin said that Teddy vomits when she is pregnant and scratches her nest like crazy before giving birth. You should pay more attention these days. "
Sure enough, two days later, the teddy began to fidget around the house, clawing at the corner of the wall with his paws. The crowd grew more nervous and came back to me. "Does Teddy have a natural birth? Have you ever delivered your Teddy? "
"No, this is the first time for me to see a dog giving birth. " At this time I was as nervous as the owner.
Finally, my mother took matters into her own hands and contacted a pet doctor friend, "Most of the time, the Teddy dog can give birth naturally, so don't panic, " the pet doctor told us in a group video. He asked the owner to give Teddy some brown sugar water and a couple of egg yolks to help Teddy build up his strength.
When Teddy had finished eating, the pet doctor went on to direct the owners. "The puppy should be almost in the pelvic cavity by now, " he said. "You pull it into a standing position on two legs with your hands, then you rub its belly and gently pull it down. Remember to move slowly. The dog is very agitated and will probably bite you."
As the group did so, Teddy slowly squeezed half an egg into a semi-transparent "Egg" , as if it were a loose egg.
I looked at the group video "Songhua eggs" , dumbfounded: "How can this be? It... It is not a chicken! "
"It's amniotic fluid wrapped around the membranes. If it stays there, the dog will probably suffocate, " the pet doctor explained. His words made us all nervous. But as time went by, the "Egg" hardly moved at all. Teddy, too, grew more agitated, and showed his teeth to the master of his flock, never allowing him to come near him again.
After about a good period of time, the "Egg" finally slowly fell to the ground. The owner immediately rushed over and ripped the fetal membranes on the surface of the egg, but there was only amniotic fluid and no sign of the puppy anywhere.
"where's the dog? " We all asked in unison.
"The puppy should still be behind it, " the pet doctor croaked. "It does happen sometimes. But that's a good thing. At least it wasn't a puppy that got stuck. "
Sure enough, Teddy followed with a loud snort, and a small dog wrapped in fetal membranes slid out of his Watergate.
After the first puppy was born, the rest of the birth went much smoother. Within two hours, four tiny black blobs, with their eyes still open, had descended into the world.
Soon after landing, the cubs can sniff their way into their mother's arms, competing to suckle, while the dog's mother sticks out her tongue and starts licking her pup.
What a lovely sight to see. It was a miracle that such a loving scene took place at a time when everyone was in danger.
Mother Teddy and her cub

Since had these a few puppy, group advocate began his immediately in friend circle"bask in WHELP"life.
Every day he posts Paparazzi videos and cute photos of the Little Guy Sleeping in various poses, from recordings of him snoring to the way he makes faces and eats.
My mother is to Meemaw, more love up my family's a lot of small things, not only often with me to fight for pet power, but also secretly give dogs to improve food behind my back. Even my beef Jerky, which she took by force, was given to the dog next door.
We soon learned that dogs don't eat as much salt as humans do. So my mom and I set off on a citywide dog food hunt.
"Don't look for it, now the express service is stopped, the shops on the street are not open, the big supermarket dog food has already sold out, where there will be dog food. " The Group of Friends Sigh. Special period, buy dog food this kind of trivial matter, incredibly also became a kind of extravagant hope. I had no choice but to make my own dog food.
Going over the research again and again, I've come up with a recipe for an epidemic dog food:
According to the recipe, I beat chicken breasts and carrots into mud with a wall breaker, add the right amount of milk and flour, and then mix into a dough, cut into pieces, and finally sent to the oven, everything is done. As the aroma wafted from the oven, little teddy in the house couldn't wait to put his nose on the stove and sniff around until his mouth was watering.
I sent my research into the group. Everyone asked me to teach a class, so I got a job as a forelock, a remote conference to guide you through the business of Shoveling Shit.
"Aunt Zhang, don't you have a kitchen scale? You put a little less chicken breast, and you probably need another small bowl of flour. "
"Brother Li, you put too much milk, how can you make noodles now? Also, don't set the oven temperature too high, or the dog food will easily get burnt. "
"sister Wang, just a moment, I'm talking to brother Li about the problem. "
In this way, I this small zoo director, suddenly changed, and became a group of well-known "Wang Chef. ".
Even I had no idea that my own "secret recipe" would be so popular with hairy children. Everyone said, or their own hand-made dog food rest assured, his dog now significantly reduced tears, hair has a luster.
I was so caught up in the excitement that I had no idea that this delicious dog food was going to turn into a disaster.

It all started with my greedy little Teddy. These days, it has been coveting his dog food "small warehouse" , from time to time will put his nose on the hearth, scanning to sniff.
One day, my mother Mongran found that the dog food on the stove was gone. A whole bag. I just made it this morning. When she went to look for it, she saw little teddy dragging a bag of dog food into his den. My mother reached out to grab it, but the food guard showed his teeth, and finally, with my cooperation, my mother, Make a sound in the east, then strike in the West, finally got the food back.
Looking at the little dog food left in the bag, my mother scowled: "eat so much, eat bad stomach how to do AH? "
Sure enough, in the middle of the night, the little guy vomited and diarrhea, ears burning. My mother was so distraught that she pulled me up without a word and rushed to the drugstore wearing a mask.
When the drugstore guide heard that we were going to buy a fever medicine, his face changed in an instant. She stepped back, then tightened and tightened the mask on her face before carefully asking, "which one of you has a fever? Is there a cough? Any other symptoms? "
My mother laughed and cried: "Comrade, do not be nervous. The fever is not us, is my family's teddy dog after eating sick. "
The shop assistant obviously didn't believe us. She cautiously pushed the glasses on the bridge of her nose, "The city government has a regulation that all patients who buy antipyretics must register their ID card number and mobile phone number. Do you have your ID card? "
I saw no room for accommodation, only braved the cold wind to go home again, from home to get me and my mother's identity cards, finally bought a box of children Cinnamomum Tamala antipyretic particles.
Before going out, the guide also repeatedly told us: "must not be careless, must pay attention to observation Ah! Now the government waived all treatment costs, you had better take the children to the People's Hospital to see it. "
I can't find the words back and forth for a moment, can only smile, hurry home. Little Teddy had taken his medicine, and he was clearly getting better. I thought we were past this.
The next morning, as soon as my mother got up, she received a phone call from a stranger.
The voice on the other end of the phone is extremely stern: "excuse me is Ms. Yang XX? "? This is the city epidemic prevention and Control Headquarters, we learned that you went to XX last night to buy a box of children Cinnamomum Tamala antipyretic particles, now want to ask you about the specific situation. How old are the kids? Do you still have a fever? What's the fever?"
My mother was asked this rapid-fire question, I and did not have time to talk to her, his cell phone also suddenly rang, the caller is still the city epidemic prevention and Control Headquarters staff.
We didn't expect the efficiency of the government to be so high. Just after we got off the phone, even the Resident Committee Lady of our community went to the door in person, she took two pictures of our family in a row, and when she was sure that none of us had a fever, she breathed a sigh of relief.
Aunt finally set foot in our home, she said in a frightened voice: "I was scared to death, fortunately only a false alarm. "

Epilogue

Right now, I'm still around the kids every day.
Sometimes I think it would be nice if everything was just a false alarm. There is no epidemic, no virus, no cousin of the far away from home, there is no countless owners and pets of the far side. But, of course, things are looking up.
My cousin was still fighting hard at the Front; my neighbor told me that his father had recovered and been discharged from the hospital, and that his mother's condition had improved. He was fully expecting the family to return safely and be reunited with the dog; the hamster's eyes were completely swollen, bestie's gray leg injury is also gradually recovering.
As spring approaches, everything will be renewed and the old diseases will be healed. Everyone in the group had agreed that when the epidemic was over, we would go and see the four little Teddy of the master, and we would run together with our young children in the bright sunshine.

Sure enough, Teddy followed with a loud snort, and a small dog wrapped in fetal membranes slid out of his Watergate.

After the first puppy was born, the rest of the birth went much smoother. Within two hours, four tiny black blobs, with their eyes still open, had descended into the world.

Soon after landing, the cubs can sniff their way into their mother's arms, competing to suckle, while the dog's mother sticks out her tongue and starts licking her pup.

What a lovely sight to see. It was a miracle that such a loving scene took place at a time when everyone was in danger.

Since had these a few puppy, group advocate began his immediately in friend circle"bask in WHELP"life.
Every day he posts Paparazzi videos and cute photos of the Little Guy Sleeping in various poses, from recordings of him snoring to the way he makes faces and eats.
My mother is to Meemaw, more love up my family's a lot of small things, not only often with me to fight for pet power, but also secretly give dogs to improve food behind my back. Even my beef Jerky, which she took by force, was given to the dog next door.
We soon learned that dogs don't eat as much salt as humans do. So my mom and I set off on a citywide dog food hunt.
"Don't look for it, now the express service is stopped, the shops on the street are not open, the big supermarket dog food has already sold out, where there will be dog food. " The Group of Friends Sigh. Special period, buy dog food this kind of trivial matter, incredibly also became a kind of extravagant hope. I had no choice but to make my own dog food.
Going over the research again and again, I've come up with a recipe for an epidemic dog food:
According to the recipe, I beat chicken breasts and carrots into mud with a wall breaker, add the right amount of milk and flour, and then mix into a dough, cut into pieces, and finally sent to the oven, everything is done. As the aroma wafted from the oven, little teddy in the house couldn't wait to put his nose on the stove and sniff around until his mouth was watering.
I sent my research into the group. Everyone asked me to teach a class, so I got a job as a forelock, a remote conference to guide you through the business of Shoveling Shit.
"Aunt Zhang, don't you have a kitchen scale? You put a little less chicken breast, and you probably need another small bowl of flour. "
"Brother Li, you put too much milk, how can you make noodles now? Also, don't set the oven temperature too high, or the dog food will easily get burnt. "
"sister Wang, just a moment, I'm talking to brother Li about the problem. "
In this way, I this small zoo director, suddenly changed, and became a group of well-known "Wang Chef. ".
Even I had no idea that my own "secret recipe" would be so popular with hairy children. Everyone said, or their own hand-made dog food rest assured, his dog now significantly reduced tears, hair has a luster.
I was so caught up in the excitement that I had no idea that this delicious dog food was going to turn into a disaster.

I was so caught up in the excitement that I had no idea that this delicious dog food was going to turn into a disaster.

It all started with my greedy little Teddy. These days, it has been coveting his dog food "small warehouse" , from time to time will put his nose on the hearth, scanning to sniff.
One day, my mother Mongran found that the dog food on the stove was gone. A whole bag. I just made it this morning. When she went to look for it, she saw little teddy dragging a bag of dog food into his den. My mother reached out to grab it, but the food guard showed his teeth, and finally, with my cooperation, my mother, Make a sound in the east, then strike in the West, finally got the food back.
Looking at the little dog food left in the bag, my mother scowled: "eat so much, eat bad stomach how to do AH? "
Sure enough, in the middle of the night, the little guy vomited and diarrhea, ears burning. My mother was so distraught that she pulled me up without a word and rushed to the drugstore wearing a mask.
When the drugstore guide heard that we were going to buy a fever medicine, his face changed in an instant. She stepped back, then tightened and tightened the mask on her face before carefully asking, "which one of you has a fever? Is there a cough? Any other symptoms? "
My mother laughed and cried: "Comrade, do not be nervous. The fever is not us, is my family's teddy dog after eating sick. "
The shop assistant obviously didn't believe us. She cautiously pushed the glasses on the bridge of her nose, "The city government has a regulation that all patients who buy antipyretics must register their ID card number and mobile phone number. Do you have your ID card? "
I saw no room for accommodation, only braved the cold wind to go home again, from home to get me and my mother's identity cards, finally bought a box of children Cinnamomum Tamala antipyretic particles.
Before going out, the guide also repeatedly told us: "must not be careless, must pay attention to observation Ah! Now the government waived all treatment costs, you had better take the children to the People's Hospital to see it. "
I can't find the words back and forth for a moment, can only smile, hurry home. Little Teddy had taken his medicine, and he was clearly getting better. I thought we were past this.
The next morning, as soon as my mother got up, she received a phone call from a stranger.
The voice on the other end of the phone is extremely stern: "excuse me is Ms. Yang XX? "? This is the city epidemic prevention and Control Headquarters, we learned that you went to XX last night to buy a box of children Cinnamomum Tamala antipyretic particles, now want to ask you about the specific situation. How old are the kids? Do you still have a fever? What's the fever?"
My mother was asked this rapid-fire question, I and did not have time to talk to her, his cell phone also suddenly rang, the caller is still the city epidemic prevention and Control Headquarters staff.
We didn't expect the efficiency of the government to be so high. Just after we got off the phone, even the Resident Committee Lady of our community went to the door in person, she took two pictures of our family in a row, and when she was sure that none of us had a fever, she breathed a sigh of relief.
Aunt finally set foot in our home, she said in a frightened voice: "I was scared to death, fortunately only a false alarm. "

Epilogue

Right now, I'm still around the kids every day.
Sometimes I think it would be nice if everything was just a false alarm. There is no epidemic, no virus, no cousin of the far away from home, there is no countless owners and pets of the far side. But, of course, things are looking up.
My cousin was still fighting hard at the Front; my neighbor told me that his father had recovered and been discharged from the hospital, and that his mother's condition had improved. He was fully expecting the family to return safely and be reunited with the dog; the hamster's eyes were completely swollen, bestie's gray leg injury is also gradually recovering.
As spring approaches, everything will be renewed and the old diseases will be healed. Everyone in the group had agreed that when the epidemic was over, we would go and see the four little Teddy of the master, and we would run together with our young children in the bright sunshine.
